Load Data

setwd("/Users/annebozack/Documents/Navas/S2_121611_run_2")

# Load Data
load("fact_funnorm_combat_data.RData")

dim(Mcombat)
# 411400     48

pheno450 = pheno


# Additional probe filtering for cross-reactive probes and probes near SNPs using DMRcate
# Setting minimum minor allele frequency to 0.05 and maximum distance from probe to 10
mFilter450 = rmSNPandCH(Mcombat, dist = 2, mafcut = 0.05, and = TRUE, rmcrosshyb = TRUE, rmXY=FALSE)
dim(mFilter450)
# 408765     48

# Exposure variable
pheno450$highAs[pheno450$expGroup == 1] = 1
pheno450$highAs[pheno450$expGroup == 0] = 0
pheno450$highAs = as.factor(pheno450$highAs)
# Check Aligment
all(pheno450$Sample_Name==colnames(mFilter450))
all(identical(pheno450$Sample_Name,colnames(mFilter450)))
# TRUE

Associations with cell type

modCD8T = lm(CD8T ~ highAs + age + Cig.Ever, data = pheno450)
modCD4T = lm(CD4T ~ highAs + age + Cig.Ever, data = pheno450)
modNK = lm(NK ~ highAs + age + Cig.Ever, data = pheno450)
modBcell = lm(Bcell ~ highAs + age + Cig.Ever, data = pheno450)
modMono = lm(Mono ~ highAs + age + Cig.Ever, data = pheno450)
modGran = lm(Gran ~ highAs + age + Cig.Ever, data = pheno450)

Categorical As models

# Unadjusted
modUnadjCat = model.matrix(~ pheno450$highAs)
                 
# Adjusted for age and smoking      
modAgeSmCat = model.matrix(~ pheno450$highAs + pheno450$age + pheno450$Cig.Ever)   
                   
# Adjusted for cell type, age, smoking
modCellAgeSmCat = model.matrix(~ pheno450$highAs + pheno450$CD8T + pheno450$CD4T + pheno450$NK + pheno450$Bcell + pheno450$Mono + pheno450$Gran + pheno450$age + pheno450$Cig.Ever)
